        <h3>Synaptic Memory &mdash; Brain-inspired Knowledge Graph</h3>
        <p class="pf-project-desc">
          A brain-inspired knowledge graph library + MCP server for LLM agents.
          With Spreading Activation (associative retrieval), Hebbian Learning (experiential learning), and 4-stage Memory Consolidation (L0~L3 auto promotion/eviction),
